questions.question:
Which of the following languages are context-free?
L_1 = {a^n b^n a^n | m, n >= 1} (note: a^n b^n a^n with same n)
L_2 = {a^m b^n c^(2n) | m, n >= 1}
L_3 = {a^m b^n | n = 2m + 1}
L_4 = {a^n b^(2n) | n >= 1}
A. L_1 and L_2 only
B. L_2 and L_3 only
C. L_3 and L_4 only
D. L_4 only

Which of the following languages is generated by the given grammar?
S -> aS | bS | epsilon
A. {a^n b^m | n, m >= 0}
B. {w | w has equal number of a's and b's}
C. {a, b}*
D. {w | w has more a's than b's}
